{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no room in the camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were told to just walk to the right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember there were these barbed wires to our right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And behind those wires were women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were shouting at us, in our own language, native language, Hungarian, asking us to throw food over the fence if we have any.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Those barbed wires of course contained high voltage electricity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anybody who would touch them would be instantly dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I remember I was with a couple of my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when we saw these women whose heads were shaved, they had some miserable, filthy piece of garment on, we looked at each other and we were firmly convinced that these women are either insane, or they're criminals, because there we were, probably about 100 to 150 yards on the other side of the tracks.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We could see the smoke coming out of the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We could smell something that, of course, we couldn't identify, but it was the smell of burning flesh.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There we were, really in the middle of the biggest death factory of modern civilization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And our minds could not understand that one human being could be treated the way those women were treated just because she happened to be born with a different religion or maybe just had one Jewish grandparent.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We just couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think this is sort of the underlying story of this whole period, that nobody believed that 20th century, civilized Germany could behave the way they believed-- behaved, because this didn't happen in a third-world country.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It wasn't a backward African country where cannibalism was the order of the day maybe 50 years before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was very civilized Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
